'''heart failure'''

# {{pathology}} The chronic inability of the [[heart]] to pump a sufficient amount of [[blood]] throughout the body, leading to a pooling of blood and shortness of breath.
# {{pathology}} The cessation of the [[heartbeat]]; [[cardiac arrest]].

